# Configure VMware vRealize Operations Management Pack for CloudHealth
After the installation, configure an instance for this management pack.
## Procedure
1. On the menu, click **Administration**.
1. In the left pane, expand **Solutions** and click **Other Accounts**.
1. Under Other Accounts, click the **ADD ACCOUNT** icon.
1. Configure the adapter instance.
1. Click **Save Settings**.
The adapter instance is added to the list.
